PSIT.BO








					About


		PS IT Infrastructure & Services Limited is an India-based company, which is engaged in trading of computer hardware and software, dealing in shares and other securities. The Company operates through two segments, including Trading in COMPUTER HARDWARE & SOFTWARE and dealing in SHARES & OTHER SECURITIES.





