Company Description                    




                        Parag Shilpa Investments Ltd. specializes in dealing with Financial activities and invest the financial resources of the company in such as securities, lend, advance or deposit, securities and property, with or without charge, interest or security, to or with such persons to receive and accept deposits, advances and loans. The company was incorporated in 1956 and is based in Mumbai.                    


